keyMappings:
# pressing y actives vomnibar with searchbar associated with y

map y Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=y

unmap [[
map > goNext #"next" link in a page

unmap ]]
map < goPrevious #"previous" link in a page

unmap >>
unmap <<

unmap ^
map - visitPreviousTab
searchEngines:
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
y: http://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
d: https://duckduckgo.com/?q=%s DuckDuckGo
m: https://www.google.com/maps?q=%s GoogleMaps
t: https://translate.google.fi/#view=home&op=translate&sl=fi&tl=en&text=%s Translate
